        "description": "<p><strong>You only need ONE PLUGIN to run your Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and other special events!<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Schedule events by date and time<\/li>\n<li>Group deals together for the event<\/li>\n<li>Create multiple events with multiple deals<\/li>\n<li>Built-in promotion designer<\/li>\n<li>Upcoming event countdown<\/li>\n<li>Event ending timer<\/li>\n<li>Order limits<\/li>\n<li>Offer BOGO deals<\/li>\n<li>Offer a fixed $10 discount<\/li>\n<li>Offer a 10% off regular price discount<\/li>\n<li>No permanent changes to products<\/li>\n<li>Offer free shipping during the event<\/li>\n<li>And more!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>**The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pimwick.com\/black-friday\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Pro version<\/a> lets you specify a custom percentage or fixed amount for the discounts. Also, you can run Buy X, Get X promos instead of just BOGO.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>We created the Black Friday plugin because we wanted an all-in-one solution for our sales events. Creating events in WooCommerce requires buying many different plugins that don&#8217;t talk to each other. This plugin handles the sale itself as well as the promotions.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Is this just for Black Friday and Cyber Monday?<\/strong><br \/>\nDefinitely not! Once we created the Black Friday plugin we realized it will work wonders for other events like Memorial Day sales, Customer Appreciation events, and more!<\/p>\n<p>We are continuing to add new features to this amazing plugin. If you have suggestions we&#8217;d love to hear it! Email <a href=\"mailto:us@pimwick.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">us@pimwick.com<\/a> and tell us what you want to see next.<\/p>\n<p>At Pimwick we LOVE making plugins that save people time and are easy to use. Contact <a href=\"mailto:us@pimwick.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">us@pimwick.com<\/a> if you have any questions!<\/p>\n<p>Compatible with WooCommerce 2.6 and higher, including 3.0+.<\/p>\n<p>Available in the following languages:<br \/>\n* Dutch<br \/>\n* French<br \/>\n* German<br \/>\n* Italian<br \/>\n* Russian<br \/>\n* Spanish<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/black-friday<\/code> directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; screen in WordPress.<\/li>\n<li>Navigate to Pimwick Plugins -&gt; Black Friday Deals<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='is%20this%20just%20for%20black%20friday%20and%20cyber%20monday%3F'>\nIs this just for Black Friday and Cyber Monday?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li>Definitely not! Once we created the Black Friday plugin we realized it will work wonders for other events like Memorial Day sales, Customer Appreciation events, and more!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='can%20i%20schedule%20a%20promotion%20that%20doesn%27t%20end%20until%20i%20stop%20it%3F'>\nCan I schedule a promotion that doesn&#8217;t end until I stop it?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li>Yes, just set the End Date far into the future and when you&#8217;re ready to end the promotion, just delete it or set the End Date to the past.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.75<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Revised tags in readme.txt<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.74<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility with WordPress 6.5 and WooCommerce 8.7<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.73<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed PHP warnings about deprecated WC_Order_Item_Coupon::offsetSet function. Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 8.4.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.72<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with High Performance Order Storage (HPOS). Fixed a potential conflict with the WooCommerce Memberships plugin. Removed a deprecated WordPress function call. PHP 8.1 compatibility changes.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.71<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with WordPress 6.4<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.70<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 8.2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.69<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 8.0 and WordPress 6.3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.68<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 7.8<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.67<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 7.5 and WordPress 6.2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.66<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added a new hook to allow prices to be overridden by custom functions: pwbf_discounted_price. Confirmed compatibility with WooCommerce 7.3.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Previous versions<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>See changelog.txt<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
